# Plan: Server API routes for text embedding & Qdrant search

## Overview
- PUT `/` — receive {t: text, g: gender, a: age}, embed with Gemini, save to Qdrant
- POST `/` — receive {t: text, g: gender, i: minage, x: maxage}, embed text, search Qdrant

